===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|bold|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|bold|lang=ang}}, {{term|blod|lang=ang}}, {{term|bolt|lang=ang}}, {{term|botl||house, dwelling-place, mansion, hall, castle, temple|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*budlą}}, {{m|gem-pro|*buþlą||house, dwelling}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*bʰew-||to grow, wax, swell}}. Cognate with {{etyl|ofs|-}} {{term|bold||house|lang=ofs}} (whence {{etyl|frr|-}} {{term|bol|lang=frr}}, {{term|boel|lang=frr}}, {{term|bøl||house|lang=frr}}), {{etyl|frr|-}} {{term|bodel|lang=frr}}, {{term|budel||property, inheritance|lang=frr}}, {{etyl|gml|-}} {{m|gml|būdel||property, real estate}}. Related to {{l/en|build}}.

